<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Dubbo - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/dubbo/</link><description>Dubbo - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/dubbo/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Dubbo RPC框架</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/dubbo/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/dubbo/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="dubbo-rpc框架">Dubbo RPC框架</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Dubbo通过注册中心实现服务自动发现，通过代理模式屏蔽远程调用细节，通过集群策略处理容错和负载均衡，是Java生态中成熟的RPC解决方案。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="dubbo通过注册中心解耦服务提供者与消费者通过代理和协议层屏蔽远程调用差异通过集群策略实现容错和负载均衡">Dubbo通过注册中心解耦服务提供者与消费者，通过代理和协议层屏蔽远程调用差异，通过集群策略实现容错和负载均衡</h2>
<h3 id="核心架构provider-consumer-registry-monitor">核心架构：Provider-Consumer-Registry-Monitor</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌─────────────┐         注册/发现          ┌─────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Provider   │ ───────────────────────→ │   Registry   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (服务提供者) │ ←─────────────────────── │  (注册中心)   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└──────┬──────┘      服务地址列表           └──────┬──────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │                                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │           RPC调用（Netty/HTTP）          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │ ←─────────────────────────────────────→ │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │                                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌──────┴──────┐                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Consumer   │                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (服务消费者) │                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└─────────────┘                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                                 │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌─────────────┐                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Monitor    │ ←───────────────────────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (监控中心)   │        调用统计上报
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└─────────────┘</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>核心角色</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Dubbo初始化对象失败（2.3版本）</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/dubbo%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/dubbo%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="dubbo初始化对象失败23版本">Dubbo初始化对象失败（2.3版本）</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Dubbo 2.3版本在Spring Boot环境下，若消费者Bean初始化早于配置中心或注册中心就绪，会导致ReferenceBean创建失败，通过调整初始化顺序、启用延迟加载或升级版本可解决。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="问题现象">问题现象</h2>
<p>服务启动报错：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanCreationException: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Error creating bean with name &#39;orderService&#39;: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Initialization of bean failed
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Caused by: java.lang.IllegalStateException: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Failed to check the status of the service xxx. 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">No provider available for the service xxx from registry xxx</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="影响范围">影响范围</h3>
<ul>
<li>服务启动失败，无法提供或消费RPC服务</li>
<li>生产环境发布时偶现，本地开发必现</li>
<li>影响服务间调用链路</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="排查过程">排查过程</h2>
<h3 id="第一步确认dubbo版本与配置">第一步：确认Dubbo版本与配置</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c"># application.yml</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">dubbo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">application</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">order-service</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">registry</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">address</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">nacos://nacos:8848</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">consumer</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">check</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">   </span><span class="c"># 启动时检查提供者是否存在</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第二步分析启动时序">第二步：分析启动时序</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Spring Boot启动流程：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 加载配置
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 创建Bean（包括Dubbo ReferenceBean）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. Dubbo尝试从注册中心查找提供者
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 若提供者未注册或网络不通 → 初始化失败
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">问题：consumer.check=true 时，引用初始化必须找到提供者</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第三步定位具体原因">第三步：定位具体原因</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>表现</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>提供者未启动</td>
          <td>消费者先启动，注册中心无服务地址</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>网络分区</td>
          <td>消费者无法连接到注册中心</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>版本不匹配</td>
          <td>消费者version/group与提供者不一致</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Nacos延迟</td>
          <td>服务注册有延迟，消费者查询时数据未同步</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="根因分析">根因分析</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Dubbo 2.3 默认行为：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ReferenceBean 初始化 → 立即连接注册中心 → 检查提供者
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                    检查失败 + check=true
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                    抛出异常，Spring容器启动失败</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>根因</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>强依赖启动顺序</td>
          <td>消费者假设提供者已就绪</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>check=true默认值</td>
          <td>2.3版本consumer.check默认true</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>同步初始化阻塞</td>
          <td>ReferenceBean在Spring启动阶段同步创建</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="解决方案">解决方案</h2>
<h3 id="方案一关闭启动检查推荐开发环境">方案一：关闭启动检查（推荐开发环境）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">dubbo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">consumer</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">check</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="w">   </span><span class="c"># 启动时不检查提供者，调用时再发现</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="方案二延迟初始化">方案二：延迟初始化</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 消费者Bean延迟加载</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@DubboReference</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">lazy</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 首次调用时才初始化代理</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrderService</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">orderService</span><span class="p">;</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="方案三指定重试与超时">方案三：指定重试与超时</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">dubbo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">consumer</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">check</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">retries</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="m">2</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">timeout</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="m">3000</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="方案四升级dubbo版本">方案四：升级Dubbo版本</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>版本</th>
          <th>改进</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>2.7+</td>
          <td>配置更灵活，支持应用级注册</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>3.0+</td>
          <td>支持Mesh、性能优化、Triple协议</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-xml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">&lt;!-- 升级到3.x --&gt;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">&lt;dependency&gt;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nt">&lt;groupId&gt;</span>org.apache.dubbo<span class="nt">&lt;/groupId&gt;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nt">&lt;artifactId&gt;</span>dubbo<span class="nt">&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nt">&lt;version&gt;</span>3.2.0<span class="nt">&lt;/version&gt;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="复盘与预防">复盘与预防</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>措施</th>
          <th>执行方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>环境差异化配置</td>
          <td>开发环境check=false，生产环境视情况</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>健康检查</td>
          <td>上线前检查提供者注册状态</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>发布顺序</td>
          <td>先发布提供者，验证后再发布消费者</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>版本管理</td>
          <td>制定Dubbo版本升级计划，避免长期停留在旧版本</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
